name: ModerateNeurologicalComplicationsWithLOSProcedures
title: Moderate Neurological Complications with LOS Procedures
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains selected moderate neurological complications procedures combined with length of stay.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients with selected moderate neurological complications procedures combined with length of stay. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD-10-PCS codes that identify patients who have selected moderate neurological complications procedures combined with length of stay.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
